P_HTM[2637]="*Tassa me saṅgho ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya chārattaṃ mānattaṃ adāsi.**and the Sangha gave me the trial period.*";
P_HTM[2638]="*Sohaṃ ciṇṇamānatto tatiyampi, bhante, saṅghaṃ abbhānaṃ yācāmī’ti.**I have now completed the trial period and for the third time I ask the Sangha for rehabilitation.’*";
P_HTM[2639]="*Byattena bhikkhunā paṭibalena saṅgho ñāpetabbo—**A competent and capable monk should then inform the Sangha:*";
P_HTM[2640]="*‘Suṇātu me, bhante, saṅgho.**‘Please, Venerables, I ask the Sangha to listen.*";
P_HTM[2641]="*Ayaṃ udāyī bhikkhu ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajji sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ appaṭicchannaṃ.**The monk Udāyī had committed one unconcealed offense of intentional emission of semen.*";
P_HTM[2642]="*So saṅghaṃ ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya chārattaṃ mānattaṃ yāci.**He asked the Sangha for the trial period of six days for that offense,*";
P_HTM[2643]="*Saṅgho udāyissa bhikkhuno ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya chārattaṃ mānattaṃ adāsi.**and the Sangha gave him the trial period.*";
P_HTM[2644]="*So ciṇṇamānatto saṅghaṃ abbhānaṃ yācati.**He’s now completed the trial period and is asking the Sangha for rehabilitation.*";
P_HTM[2645]="*Yadi saṅghassa pattakallaṃ, saṅgho udāyiṃ bhikkhuṃ abbheyya.**If it seems appropriate to the Sangha, the Sangha should rehabilitate him.*";
P_HTM[2646]="*Esā ñatti.**This is the motion.*";
P_HTM[2647]="*Suṇātu me, bhante, saṅgho.**Please, Venerables, I ask the Sangha to listen.*";
