P_HTM[2649]="*So saṅghaṃ ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya chārattaṃ mānattaṃ yāci.**He asked the Sangha for the trial period of six days for that offense,*";
