P_HTM[2705]="*So parivutthaparivāso bhikkhūnaṃ ārocesi—**When he had completed the probation, he told the monks,*";
P_HTM[2706]="*“ahaṃ, āvuso, ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ ekāhappaṭicchannaṃ.**“I had committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for one day.*";
