P_HTM[2740]="*Dinnaṃ saṅghena udāyissa bhikkhuno ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā ekāhappaṭicchannāya chārattaṃ mānattaṃ.**The Sangha has given the monk Udāyī the trial period of six days for one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for one day.*";
P_HTM[2741]="*Khamati saṅghassa, tasmā tuṇhī, evametaṃ dhārayāmī’”ti.**The Sangha approves and is therefore silent. I will remember it thus.’”*";
P_HTM[2742]="*1.5. Ekāhappaṭicchannaabbhāna**1.5 Rehabilitation for those with offenses concealed for one day*";
P_HTM[2743]="*So ciṇṇamānatto bhikkhūnaṃ ārocesi—**When he had completed the trial period, he told the monks,*";
P_HTM[2744]="*“ahaṃ, āvuso, ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ ekāhappaṭicchannaṃ.**“I had committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for one day.*";
P_HTM[2745]="*Sohaṃ saṅghaṃ ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā ekāhappaṭicchannāya ekāhaparivāsaṃ yāciṃ.**I asked the Sangha for probation for one day for that offense,*";
P_HTM[2746]="*Tassa me saṅgho ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā ekāhappaṭicchannāya ekāhaparivāsaṃ adāsi.**and the Sangha gave me that probation.*";
P_HTM[2747]="*Sohaṃ parivutthaparivāso saṅghaṃ ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā ekāhappaṭicchannāya chārattaṃ mānattaṃ yāciṃ.**When I had completed the probation, I asked the Sangha for the trial period of six days for that offense.*";
P_HTM[2748]="*Tassa me saṅgho ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā ekāhappaṭicchannāya chārattaṃ mānattaṃ adāsi.**The Sangha gave me the trial period,*";
P_HTM[2749]="*Sohaṃ ciṇṇamānatto.**and I have now completed it.*";
P_HTM[2750]="*Kathaṃ nu kho mayā paṭipajjitabban”ti?**What should I do now?”*";
P_HTM[2751]="*Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ.**They told the Buddha.*";
P_HTM[2752]="*“Tena hi, bhikkhave, saṅgho udāyiṃ bhikkhuṃ abbhetu.**“Well then, the Sangha should rehabilitate the monk Udāyī.*";
P_HTM[2753]="*Evañca pana, bhikkhave, abbhetabbo—**And it should be done like this:*";
P_HTM[2754]="*Tena, bhikkhave, udāyinā bhikkhunā saṅghaṃ upasaṅkamitvā …pe…**The monk Udāyī should approach the Sangha, put his upper robe over one shoulder, pay respect at the feet of the senior monks, squat on his heels, raise his joined palms,*";
P_HTM[2755]="*evamassa vacanīyo—**and say:*";
P_HTM[2756]="*‘ahaṃ, bhante, ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ ekāhappaṭicchannaṃ.**‘I had committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for one day.*";
P_HTM[2757]="*Sohaṃ saṅghaṃ ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā ekāhappaṭicchannāya ekāhaparivāsaṃ yāciṃ.**I asked the Sangha for probation for one day for that offense,*";
P_HTM[2758]="*Tassa me saṅgho ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā ekāhappaṭicchannāya ekāhaparivāsaṃ adāsi.**and the Sangha gave me that probation.*";
P_HTM[2759]="*Sohaṃ parivutthaparivāso saṅghaṃ ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā ekāhappaṭicchannāya chārattaṃ mānattaṃ yāciṃ.**When I had completed the probation, I asked the Sangha for the trial period of six days for that offense,*";
P_HTM[2760]="*Tassa me saṅgho ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā ekāhappaṭicchannāya chārattaṃ mānattaṃ adāsi.**and the Sangha gave me the trial period.*";
P_HTM[2761]="*Sohaṃ, bhante, ciṇṇamānatto saṅghaṃ abbhānaṃ yācāmī’ti.**I have now completed the trial period and I ask the Sangha for rehabilitation.’*";
P_HTM[2762]="*Dutiyampi yācitabbaṃ.**And he should ask a second*";
P_HTM[2763]="*Tatiyampi yācitabbaṃ.**and a third time.*";
P_HTM[2764]="*Byattena bhikkhunā paṭibalena saṅgho ñāpetabbo—**A competent and capable monk should then inform the Sangha:*";
P_HTM[2765]="*‘Suṇātu me, bhante, saṅgho.**‘Please, Venerables, I ask the Sangha to listen.*";
P_HTM[2766]="*Ayaṃ udāyī bhikkhu ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajji sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ ekāhappaṭicchannaṃ.**The monk Udāyī had committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for one day.*";
P_HTM[2767]="*So saṅghaṃ ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā ekāhappaṭicchannāya ekāhaparivāsaṃ yāci.**He asked the Sangha for probation for one day for that offense,*";
P_HTM[2768]="*Saṅgho udāyissa bhikkhuno ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā ekāhappaṭicchannāya ekāhaparivāsaṃ adāsi.**and the Sangha gave him that probation.*";
P_HTM[2769]="*So parivutthaparivāso saṅghaṃ ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā ekāhappaṭicchannāya chārattaṃ mānattaṃ yāci.**When he had completed the probation, he asked the Sangha for the trial period of six days for that offense,*";
P_HTM[2770]="*Saṅgho udāyissa bhikkhuno ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā ekāhappaṭicchannāya chārattaṃ mānattaṃ adāsi.**and the Sangha gave him the trial period.*";
P_HTM[2771]="*So ciṇṇamānatto saṅghaṃ abbhānaṃ yācati.**He’s now completed the trial period and is asking the Sangha for rehabilitation.*";
P_HTM[2772]="*Yadi saṅghassa pattakallaṃ, saṅgho udāyiṃ bhikkhuṃ abbheyya.**If it seems appropriate to the Sangha, the Sangha should rehabilitate him.*";
P_HTM[2773]="*Esā ñatti.**This is the motion.*";
P_HTM[2774]="*Suṇātu me, bhante, saṅgho.**Please, Venerables, I ask the Sangha to listen.*";
P_HTM[2775]="*Ayaṃ udāyī bhikkhu ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajji sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ ekāhappaṭicchannaṃ.**The monk Udāyī had committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for one day.*";
P_HTM[2776]="*So saṅghaṃ ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā ekāhappaṭicchannāya ekāhaparivāsaṃ yāci.**He asked the Sangha for probation for one day for that offense,*";
P_HTM[2777]="*Saṅgho udāyissa bhikkhuno ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā ekāhappaṭicchannāya ekāhaparivāsaṃ adāsi.**and the Sangha gave him that probation.*";
P_HTM[2778]="*So parivutthaparivāso saṅghaṃ ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā ekāhappaṭicchannāya chārattaṃ mānattaṃ yāci.**When he had completed the probation, he asked the Sangha for the trial period of six days for that offense,*";
P_HTM[2779]="*Saṅgho udāyissa bhikkhuno ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā ekāhappaṭicchannāya chārattaṃ mānattaṃ adāsi.**and the Sangha gave him the trial period.*";
P_HTM[2780]="*So ciṇṇamānatto saṅghaṃ abbhānaṃ yācati.**He’s now completed the trial period and is asking the Sangha for rehabilitation.*";
P_HTM[2781]="*Saṅgho udāyiṃ bhikkhuṃ abbheti.**The Sangha rehabilitates him.*";
P_HTM[2782]="*Yassāyasmato khamati udāyissa bhikkhuno abbhānaṃ, so tuṇhassa;**Any monk who approves of rehabilitating him should remain silent.*";
P_HTM[2783]="*yassa nakkhamati, so bhāseyya.**Any monk who does not approve should speak up.*";
P_HTM[2784]="*Dutiyampi etamatthaṃ vadāmi …pe…**For the second time I speak on this matter. …*";
P_HTM[2785]="*tatiyampi etamatthaṃ vadāmi …pe….**For the third time I speak on this matter. …*";
P_HTM[2786]="*Abbhito saṅghena udāyī bhikkhu.**The Sangha has rehabilitated the monk Udāyī.*";
P_HTM[2787]="*Khamati saṅghassa, tasmā tuṇhī, evametaṃ dhārayāmī’”ti.**The Sangha approves and is therefore silent. I will remember it thus.’”*";
P_HTM[2788]="*1.6. Pañcāhappaṭicchannaparivāsa**1.6 Probation for those with offenses concealed for five days*";
P_HTM[2789]="*Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā udāyī ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpanno hoti sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ dvīhappaṭicchannaṃ …pe…**On one occasion Venerable Udāyī had committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for two days. …*";
P_HTM[2790]="*tīhappaṭicchannaṃ …pe…**concealed for three days. …*";
P_HTM[2791]="*catūhappaṭicchannaṃ …pe…**concealed for four days. …*";
P_HTM[2792]="*pañcāhappaṭicchannaṃ.**concealed for five days.*";
P_HTM[2793]="*So bhikkhūnaṃ ārocesi—**He told the monks about this,*";
P_HTM[2794]="*“ahaṃ, āvuso, ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pañcāhappaṭicchannaṃ.* **";
P_HTM[2795]="*Kathaṃ nu kho mayā paṭipajjitabban”ti?**adding, “What should I do now?”*";
P_HTM[2796]="*Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ.**They told the Buddha.*";
P_HTM[2797]="*“Tena hi, bhikkhave, saṅgho udāyissa bhikkhuno ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya pañcāhaparivāsaṃ detu.**“Well then, the Sangha should give the monk Udāyī probation for five days for one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for five days.*";
P_HTM[2798]="*Evañca pana, bhikkhave, dātabbo—**And it should be given like this:*";
P_HTM[2799]="*Tena, bhikkhave, udāyinā bhikkhunā saṅghaṃ upasaṅkamitvā ekaṃsaṃ uttarāsaṅgaṃ karitvā vuḍḍhānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ pāde vanditvā ukkuṭikaṃ nisīditvā añjaliṃ paggahetvā evamassa vacanīyo—**The monk Udāyī should approach the Sangha, put his upper robe over one shoulder, pay respect at the feet of the senior monks, squat on his heels, raise his joined palms, and say:*";
P_HTM[2800]="*‘ahaṃ, bhante, ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pañcāhappaṭicchannaṃ.**‘Venerables, I have committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for five days.*";
P_HTM[2801]="*Sohaṃ, bhante, saṅghaṃ ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya pañcāhaparivāsaṃ yācāmī’ti.**I ask the Sangha for probation for five days for that offense.’*";
P_HTM[2802]="*Dutiyampi yācitabbo.**And he should ask a second*";
P_HTM[2803]="*Tatiyampi yācitabbo.**and a third time.*";
P_HTM[2804]="*Byattena bhikkhunā paṭibalena saṅgho ñāpetabbo—**A competent and capable monk should then inform the Sangha:*";
P_HTM[2805]="*‘Suṇātu me, bhante, saṅgho.**‘Please, Venerables, I ask the Sangha to listen.*";
P_HTM[2806]="*Ayaṃ udāyī bhikkhu ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajji sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pañcāhappaṭicchannaṃ.**The monk Udāyī has committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for five days.*";
P_HTM[2807]="*So saṅghaṃ ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya pañcāhaparivāsaṃ yācati.**He is asking the Sangha for probation for five days for that offense.*";
P_HTM[2808]="*Yadi saṅghassa pattakallaṃ, saṅgho udāyissa bhikkhuno ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya pañcāhaparivāsaṃ dadeyya.**If it seems appropriate to the Sangha, the Sangha should give him that probation.*";
P_HTM[2809]="*Esā ñatti.**This is the motion.*";
P_HTM[2810]="*Suṇātu me, bhante, saṅgho.**Please, Venerables, I ask the Sangha to listen.*";
P_HTM[2811]="*Ayaṃ udāyī bhikkhu ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajji sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pañcāhappaṭicchannaṃ.**The monk Udāyī has committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for five days.*";
P_HTM[2812]="*So saṅghaṃ ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya pañcāhaparivāsaṃ yācati.**He is asking the Sangha for probation for five days for that offense.*";
P_HTM[2813]="*Saṅgho udāyissa bhikkhuno ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya pañcāhaparivāsaṃ deti.**The Sangha gives him that probation.*";
P_HTM[2814]="*Yassāyasmato khamati udāyissa bhikkhuno ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya pañcāhaparivāsassa dānaṃ, so tuṇhassa;**Any monk who approves of giving him that probation should remain silent.*";
P_HTM[2815]="*yassa nakkhamati, so bhāseyya.**Any monk who does not approve should speak up.*";
P_HTM[2816]="*Dutiyampi etamatthaṃ vadāmi …pe…**For the second time I speak on this matter. …*";
P_HTM[2817]="*tatiyampi etamatthaṃ vadāmi …pe….**For the third time I speak on this matter. …*";
P_HTM[2818]="*Dinno saṅghena udāyissa bhikkhuno ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya pañcāhaparivāso.**The Sangha has given the monk Udāyī probation for five days for one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for five days.*";
P_HTM[2819]="*Khamati saṅghassa, tasmā tuṇhī, evametaṃ dhārayāmī’”ti.**The Sangha approves and is therefore silent. I will remember it thus.’”*";
P_HTM[2820]="*1.7. Pārivāsikamūlāyapaṭikassanā**1.7 Sending back to the beginning of those on probation*";
P_HTM[2821]="*So parivasanto antarā ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajji sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ appaṭicchannaṃ.**While he was on probation, he committed one unconcealed offense of intentional emission of semen.*";
P_HTM[2822]="*So bhikkhūnaṃ ārocesi—**He told the monks,*";
P_HTM[2823]="*“ahaṃ, āvuso, ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pañcāhappaṭicchannaṃ.**“I had committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for five days.*";
P_HTM[2824]="*Sohaṃ saṅghaṃ ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya pañcāhaparivāsaṃ yāciṃ.**I asked the Sangha for probation for five days for that offense,*";
P_HTM[2825]="*Tassa me saṅgho ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya pañcāhaparivāsaṃ adāsi.**and the Sangha gave me that probation.*";
P_HTM[2826]="*Sohaṃ parivasanto antarā ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ appaṭicchannaṃ.**While on probation, I committed one unconcealed offense of intentional emission of semen.*";
P_HTM[2827]="*Kathaṃ nu kho mayā paṭipajjitabban”ti?**What should I do now?”*";
P_HTM[2828]="*Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ.**They told the Buddha.*";
P_HTM[2829]="*“Tena hi, bhikkhave, saṅgho udāyiṃ bhikkhuṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya mūlāya paṭikassatu.**“Well then, the Sangha should send the monk Udāyī back to the beginning for one unconcealed offense of intentional emission of semen, committed while on probation.*";
P_HTM[2830]="*Evañca pana, bhikkhave, mūlāya paṭikassitabbo—**And it should be done like this:*";
P_HTM[2831]="*Tena, bhikkhave, udāyinā bhikkhunā saṅghaṃ upasaṅkamitvā …pe…**The monk Udāyī should approach the Sangha, put his upper robe over one shoulder, pay respect at the feet of the senior monks, squat on his heels, raise his joined palms,*";
P_HTM[2832]="*evamassa vacanīyo—**and say:*";
P_HTM[2833]="*‘ahaṃ, bhante, ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pañcāhappaṭicchannaṃ.**‘Venerables, I had committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for five days.*";
P_HTM[2834]="*Sohaṃ saṅghaṃ ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya pañcāhaparivāsaṃ yāciṃ.**I asked the Sangha for probation for five days for that offense,*";
P_HTM[2835]="*Tassa me saṅgho ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya pañcāhaparivāsaṃ adāsi.**and the Sangha gave me that probation.*";
P_HTM[2836]="*Sohaṃ parivasanto antarā ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ appaṭicchannaṃ.**While on probation, I committed one unconcealed offense of intentional emission of semen.*";
