P_HTM[2844]="*Saṅgho udāyissa bhikkhuno ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya pañcāhaparivāsaṃ adāsi.**and the Sangha gave him that probation.*";
P_HTM[2845]="*So parivasanto antarā ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajji sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ appaṭicchannaṃ.**While he was on probation, he committed one unconcealed offense of intentional emission of semen.*";
