P_HTM[2851]="*So saṅghaṃ ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya pañcāhaparivāsaṃ yāci.**He asked the Sangha for probation for five days for that offense,*";
P_HTM[2852]="*Saṅgho udāyissa bhikkhuno ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya pañcāhaparivāsaṃ adāsi.**and the Sangha gave him that probation.*";
P_HTM[2853]="*So parivasanto antarā ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajji sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ appaṭicchannaṃ.**While he was on probation, he committed one unconcealed offense of intentional emission of semen.*";
P_HTM[2854]="*So saṅghaṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya mūlāyapaṭikassanaṃ yācati.**He is now asking the Sangha to send him back to the beginning for that offense.*";
P_HTM[2855]="*Saṅgho udāyiṃ bhikkhuṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya mūlāya paṭikassati.**The Sangha sends him back to the beginning.*";
P_HTM[2856]="*Yassāyasmato khamati udāyissa bhikkhuno antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya mūlāyapaṭikassanā, so tuṇhassa;**Any monk who approves of sending him back to the beginning should remain silent.*";
P_HTM[2857]="*yassa nakkhamati, so bhāseyya.**Any monk who does not approve should speak up.*";
P_HTM[2858]="*Dutiyampi etamatthaṃ vadāmi …pe…**For the second time I speak on this matter. …*";
P_HTM[2859]="*tatiyampi etamatthaṃ vadāmi …pe….**For the third time I speak on this matter. …*";
P_HTM[2860]="*Paṭikassito saṅghena udāyī bhikkhu antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya mūlāyapaṭikassanā.**The Sangha has sent the monk Udāyī back to the beginning for one unconcealed offense of intentional emission of semen, committed while on probation.*";
P_HTM[2861]="*Khamati saṅghassa, tasmā tuṇhī, evametaṃ dhārayāmī’”ti.**The Sangha approves and is therefore silent. I will remember it thus.’”*";
P_HTM[2862]="*1.8. Mānattārahamūlāyapaṭikassanā**1.8 Sending back to the beginning of those deserving the trial period*";
P_HTM[2863]="*So parivutthaparivāso mānattāraho antarā ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajji sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ appaṭicchannaṃ.**When he had completed the probation, while deserving the trial period, he committed one unconcealed offense of intentional emission of semen.*";
P_HTM[2864]="*So bhikkhūnaṃ ārocesi—**He told the monks,*";
P_HTM[2865]="*“ahaṃ, āvuso, ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pañcāhappaṭicchannaṃ.**“I had committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for five days.*";
P_HTM[2866]="*Sohaṃ saṅghaṃ ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya pañcāhaparivāsaṃ yāciṃ.**I asked the Sangha for probation for five days for that offense,*";
P_HTM[2867]="*Tassa me saṅgho ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya pañcāhaparivāsaṃ adāsi.**and the Sangha gave me that probation.*";
P_HTM[2868]="*Sohaṃ parivasanto antarā ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ appaṭicchannaṃ.**While on probation, I committed one unconcealed offense of intentional emission of semen.*";
P_HTM[2869]="*Sohaṃ saṅghaṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya mūlāyapaṭikassanaṃ yāciṃ.**I asked the Sangha to send me back to the beginning for that offense,*";
P_HTM[2870]="*Taṃ maṃ saṅgho antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya mūlāya paṭikassi.**and the Sangha sent me back to the beginning.*";
P_HTM[2871]="*Sohaṃ parivutthaparivāso mānattāraho antarā ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ appaṭicchannaṃ.**When I had completed the probation, while deserving the trial period, I committed one unconcealed offense of intentional emission of semen.*";
P_HTM[2872]="*Kathaṃ nu kho mayā paṭipajjitabban”ti?**What should I do now?”*";
P_HTM[2873]="*Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ.**They told the Buddha.*";
P_HTM[2874]="*“Tena hi, bhikkhave, saṅgho udāyiṃ bhikkhuṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya mūlāya paṭikassatu.**“Well then, the Sangha should send the monk Udāyī back to the beginning for one unconcealed offense of intentional emission of semen, committed while deserving the trial period.*";
P_HTM[2875]="*Evañca pana, bhikkhave, mūlāya paṭikassitabbo—**And it should be done like this:*";
P_HTM[2876]="*Tena, bhikkhave, udāyinā bhikkhunā saṅghaṃ upasaṅkamitvā …pe…**The monk Udāyī should approach the Sangha, put his upper robe over one shoulder, pay respect at the feet of the senior monks, squat on his heels, raise his joined palms,*";
P_HTM[2877]="*evamassa vacanīyo—**and say:*";
P_HTM[2878]="*‘ahaṃ, bhante, ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pañcāhappaṭicchannaṃ …pe…**‘Venerables, I had committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for five days. …*";
P_HTM[2879]="*sohaṃ parivutthaparivāso mānattāraho antarā ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ appaṭicchannaṃ.**When I had completed the probation, while deserving the trial period, I committed one unconcealed offense of intentional emission of semen.*";
P_HTM[2880]="*Sohaṃ saṅghaṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya mūlāyapaṭikassanaṃ yācāmī’ti.**I ask the Sangha to send me back to the beginning for that offense, committed while deserving the trial period.’*";
P_HTM[2881]="*Dutiyampi yācitabbā.**And he should ask a second*";
P_HTM[2882]="*Tatiyampi yācitabbā.**and a third time.*";
P_HTM[2883]="*Byattena bhikkhunā paṭibalena saṅgho ñāpetabbo—**A competent and capable monk should then inform the Sangha:*";
P_HTM[2884]="*‘Suṇātu me, bhante, saṅgho.**‘Please, Venerables, I ask the Sangha to listen.*";
P_HTM[2885]="*Ayaṃ udāyī bhikkhu ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajji sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pañcāhappaṭicchannaṃ …pe…**The monk Udāyī had committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for five days. …*";
P_HTM[2886]="*so parivutthaparivāso mānattāraho antarā ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajji sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ appaṭicchannaṃ.**When he had completed the probation, while deserving the trial period, he committed one unconcealed offense of intentional emission of semen.*";
P_HTM[2887]="*So saṅghaṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya mūlāyapaṭikassanaṃ yācati.**He is asking the Sangha to send him back to the beginning for that offense, committed while deserving the trial period.*";
P_HTM[2888]="*Yadi saṅghassa pattakallaṃ, saṅgho udāyiṃ bhikkhuṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya mūlāya paṭikasseyya.**If it seems appropriate to the Sangha, the Sangha should send him back to the beginning.*";
P_HTM[2889]="*Esā ñatti.**This is the motion.*";
P_HTM[2890]="*Suṇātu me, bhante, saṅgho.**Please, Venerables, I ask the Sangha to listen.*";
P_HTM[2891]="*Ayaṃ udāyī bhikkhu ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajji sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pañcāhappaṭicchannaṃ …pe…**The monk Udāyī had committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for five days. …*";
