P_HTM[2902]="*So parivutthaparivāso bhikkhūnaṃ ārocesi—**When he had completed the probation, he told the monks,*";
P_HTM[2903]="*“ahaṃ, āvuso, ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pañcāhappaṭicchannaṃ …pe…**“I had committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for five days …*";
P_HTM[2904]="*sohaṃ parivutthaparivāso.**I have now completed the probation.*";
