P_HTM[2965]="*Dutiyampi yācitabbaṃ.**And he should ask a second*";
P_HTM[2966]="*Tatiyampi yācitabbaṃ.**and a third time.*";
P_HTM[2967]="*Byattena bhikkhunā paṭibalena saṅgho ñāpetabbo—**A competent and capable monk should then inform the Sangha:*";
P_HTM[2968]="*‘Suṇātu me, bhante, saṅgho.**‘Please, Venerables, I ask the Sangha to listen.*";
P_HTM[2969]="*Ayaṃ udāyī bhikkhu …pe…**The monk Udāyī …*";
P_HTM[2970]="*chārattaṃ mānattaṃ yācati.**is asking the Sangha for the trial period of six days for that offense, committed while undertaking the trial period.*";
P_HTM[2971]="*Yadi saṅghassa pattakallaṃ, saṅgho udāyissa bhikkhuno antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya chārattaṃ mānattaṃ dadeyya.**If it seems appropriate to the Sangha, the Sangha should give him the trial period of six days.*";
P_HTM[2972]="*Esā ñatti …pe…**This is the motion. …*";
P_HTM[2973]="*Dinnaṃ saṅghena udāyissa bhikkhuno antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya chārattaṃ mānattaṃ.**The Sangha has given the monk Udāyī the trial period of six days for one unconcealed offense of intentional emission of semen, committed while undertaking the trial period.*";
P_HTM[2974]="*Khamati saṅghassa, tasmā tuṇhī, evametaṃ dhārayāmī’”ti.**The Sangha approves and is therefore silent. I will remember it thus.’”*";
P_HTM[2975]="*1.11. Abbhānārahamūlāyapaṭikassanā**1.11 Sending back to the beginning of those deserving rehabilitation*";
P_HTM[2976]="*So ciṇṇamānatto abbhānāraho antarā ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajji sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ appaṭicchannaṃ.**When he had completed the trial period, while deserving rehabilitation, he committed one unconcealed offense of intentional emission of semen.*";
P_HTM[2977]="*So bhikkhūnaṃ ārocesi—**He told the monks,*";
P_HTM[2978]="*“ahaṃ, āvuso, ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pañcāhappaṭicchannaṃ …pe…**“I had committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for five days. …*";
P_HTM[2979]="*sohaṃ ciṇṇamānatto abbhānāraho antarā ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ appaṭicchannaṃ.**When I had completed the trial period, while deserving rehabilitation, I committed one unconcealed offense of intentional emission of semen.*";
P_HTM[2980]="*Kathaṃ nu kho mayā paṭipajjitabban”ti?**What should I do now?”*";
P_HTM[2981]="*Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ.**They told the Buddha.*";
P_HTM[2982]="*“Tena hi, bhikkhave, saṅgho udāyiṃ bhikkhuṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya mūlāya paṭikassitvā chārattaṃ mānattaṃ detu.**“Well then, the Sangha should send the monk Udāyī back to the beginning for one unconcealed offense of intentional emission of semen, committed while deserving rehabilitation. It should then give him the trial period of six days.*";
P_HTM[2983]="*Evañca pana, bhikkhave, mūlāya paṭikassitabbo …pe….**And he should be sent back to the beginning like this: …*";
P_HTM[2984]="*Evañca pana, bhikkhave, chārattaṃ mānattaṃ dātabbaṃ …pe….**And he should be given the trial period of six days like this: …*";
P_HTM[2985]="*Dinnaṃ saṅghena udāyissa bhikkhuno antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya chārattaṃ mānattaṃ.**The Sangha has given the monk Udāyī the trial period of six days for one unconcealed offense of intentional emission of semen, committed while deserving rehabilitation.*";
P_HTM[2986]="*Khamati saṅghassa, tasmā tuṇhī, evametaṃ dhārayāmī’”ti.**The Sangha approves and is therefore silent. I will remember it thus.’”*";
P_HTM[2987]="*1.12. Mūlāyapaṭikassitaabbhāna**1.12 Rehabilitation of those sent back to the beginning*";
P_HTM[2988]="*So ciṇṇamānatto bhikkhūnaṃ ārocesi—**When he had completed the trial period, he told the monks,*";
P_HTM[2989]="*“ahaṃ, āvuso, ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pañcāhappaṭicchannaṃ …pe…**“I had committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for five days. …*";
P_HTM[2990]="*sohaṃ ciṇṇamānatto.**I have now completed the trial period.*";
P_HTM[2991]="*Kathaṃ nu kho mayā paṭipajjitabban”ti?**What should I do now?”*";
P_HTM[2992]="*Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ.**They told the Buddha.*";
P_HTM[2993]="*“Tena hi, bhikkhave, saṅgho udāyiṃ bhikkhuṃ abbhetu.**“Well then, the Sangha should rehabilitate the monk Udāyī.*";
P_HTM[2994]="*Evañca pana, bhikkhave, abbhetabbo—**And it should be done like this:*";
P_HTM[2995]="*Tena, bhikkhave, udāyinā bhikkhunā saṅghaṃ upasaṅkamitvā …pe…**The monk Udāyī should approach the Sangha, put his upper robe over one shoulder, pay respect at the feet of the senior monks, squat on his heels, raise his joined palms,*";
P_HTM[2996]="*evamassa vacanīyo—**and say:*";
P_HTM[2997]="*‘ahaṃ, bhante, ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pañcāhappaṭicchannaṃ.**‘Venerables, I had committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for five days.*";
P_HTM[2998]="*Sohaṃ saṅghaṃ ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya pañcāhaparivāsaṃ yāciṃ.**I asked the Sangha for probation for five days for that offense,*";
P_HTM[2999]="*Tassa me saṅgho ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya pañcāhaparivāsaṃ adāsi.**and the Sangha gave me that probation.*";
P_HTM[3000]="*Sohaṃ parivasanto antarā ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ appaṭicchannaṃ.**While on probation, I committed one unconcealed offense of intentional emission of semen.*";
P_HTM[3001]="*Sohaṃ saṅghaṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya mūlāyapaṭikassanaṃ yāciṃ.**I asked the Sangha to send me back to the beginning for that offense,*";
P_HTM[3002]="*Taṃ maṃ saṅgho antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya mūlāya paṭikassi.**which it did.*";
P_HTM[3003]="*Sohaṃ parivutthaparivāso mānattāraho antarā ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ appaṭicchannaṃ.**When I had completed the probation, while deserving the trial period, I committed one unconcealed offense of intentional emission of semen.*";
P_HTM[3004]="*Sohaṃ saṅghaṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya mūlāyapaṭikassanaṃ yāciṃ.**I asked the Sangha to send me back to the beginning for that offense,*";
P_HTM[3005]="*Taṃ maṃ saṅgho antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya mūlāya paṭikassi.**which it did.*";
P_HTM[3006]="*Sohaṃ parivutthaparivāso saṅghaṃ tissannaṃ āpattīnaṃ chārattaṃ mānattaṃ yāciṃ.**When I had completed the probation, I asked the Sangha for the trial period of six days for the three offenses,*";
P_HTM[3007]="*Tassa me saṅgho tissannaṃ āpattīnaṃ chārattaṃ mānattaṃ adāsi.**and the Sangha gave me the trial period.*";
P_HTM[3008]="*Sohaṃ mānattaṃ caranto antarā ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ appaṭicchannaṃ.**While undertaking the trial period, I committed one unconcealed offense of intentional emission of semen.*";
P_HTM[3009]="*Sohaṃ saṅghaṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya mūlāyapaṭikassanaṃ yāciṃ.**I asked the Sangha to send me back to the beginning for that offense,*";
P_HTM[3010]="*Taṃ maṃ saṅgho antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya mūlāya paṭikassi.**which it did.*";
P_HTM[3011]="*Sohaṃ saṅghaṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya chārattaṃ mānattaṃ yāciṃ.**I then asked the Sangha to give me the trial period for that offense,*";
P_HTM[3012]="*Tassa me saṅgho antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya chārattaṃ mānattaṃ adāsi.**which it did.*";
P_HTM[3013]="*Sohaṃ ciṇṇamānatto abbhānāraho antarā ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ appaṭicchannaṃ.**When I had completed the trial period, while deserving rehabilitation, I committed one unconcealed offense of intentional emission of semen.*";
P_HTM[3014]="*Sohaṃ saṅghaṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya mūlāyapaṭikassanaṃ yāciṃ.**I asked the Sangha to send me back to the beginning for that offense,*";
P_HTM[3015]="*Taṃ maṃ saṅgho antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya mūlāya paṭikassi.**which it did.*";
P_HTM[3016]="*Sohaṃ saṅghaṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya chārattaṃ mānattaṃ yāciṃ.**I then asked the Sangha to give me the trial period for that offense,*";
P_HTM[3017]="*Tassa me saṅgho antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya chārattaṃ mānattaṃ adāsi.**which it gave me.*";
P_HTM[3018]="*Sohaṃ, bhante, ciṇṇamānatto saṅghaṃ abbhānaṃ yācāmī’ti.**I have now completed the trial period and I ask the Sangha for rehabilitation.’*";
P_HTM[3019]="*Dutiyampi yācitabbaṃ.**And he should ask a second*";
P_HTM[3020]="*Tatiyampi yācitabbaṃ.**and a third time.*";
P_HTM[3021]="*Byattena bhikkhunā paṭibalena saṅgho ñāpetabbo—**A competent and capable monk should then inform the Sangha:*";
P_HTM[3022]="*‘Suṇātu me, bhante, saṅgho.**‘Please, Venerables, I ask the Sangha to listen.*";
P_HTM[3023]="*Ayaṃ udāyī bhikkhu ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajji sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pañcāhappaṭicchannaṃ.**The monk Udāyī had committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for five days.*";
P_HTM[3024]="*So saṅghaṃ ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya pañcāhaparivāsaṃ yāci.**He asked the Sangha for probation for five days for that offense,*";
P_HTM[3025]="*Saṅgho udāyissa bhikkhuno ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya pañcāhaparivāsaṃ adāsi.**and the Sangha gave him that probation.*";
P_HTM[3026]="*So parivasanto antarā ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajji sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ appaṭicchannaṃ.**While he was on probation, he committed one unconcealed offense of intentional emission of semen.*";
P_HTM[3027]="*So saṅghaṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya mūlāyapaṭikassanaṃ yāci.**He asked the Sangha to send him back to the beginning for that offense,*";
P_HTM[3028]="*Saṅgho udāyiṃ bhikkhuṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya mūlāya paṭikassi.**which it did.*";
P_HTM[3029]="*So parivutthaparivāso mānattāraho antarā ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajji sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ appaṭicchannaṃ.**When he had completed the probation, while deserving the trial period, he committed one unconcealed offense of intentional emission of semen.*";
P_HTM[3030]="*So saṅghaṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya mūlāyapaṭikassanaṃ yāci.**He asked the Sangha to send him back to the beginning for that offense,*";
P_HTM[3031]="*Saṅgho udāyiṃ bhikkhuṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya mūlāya paṭikassi.**which it did.*";
P_HTM[3032]="*So parivutthaparivāso saṅghaṃ tissannaṃ āpattīnaṃ chārattaṃ mānattaṃ yāci.**When he had completed the probation, he asked the Sangha for the trial period of six days for the three offenses,*";
P_HTM[3033]="*Saṅgho udāyissa bhikkhuno tissannaṃ āpattīnaṃ chārattaṃ mānattaṃ adāsi.**and the Sangha gave him the trial period.*";
P_HTM[3034]="*So mānattaṃ caranto antarā ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajji sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ appaṭicchannaṃ.**While he was undertaking the trial period, he committed one unconcealed offense of intentional emission of semen.*";
P_HTM[3035]="*So saṅghaṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya mūlāyapaṭikassanaṃ yāci.**He asked the Sangha to send him back to the beginning for that offense,*";
P_HTM[3036]="*Saṅgho udāyiṃ bhikkhuṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya mūlāya paṭikassi.**which it did.*";
P_HTM[3037]="*So saṅghaṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya chārattaṃ mānattaṃ yāci.**He then asked the Sangha to give him the trial period for that offense,*";
P_HTM[3038]="*Saṅgho udāyissa bhikkhuno antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya chārattaṃ mānattaṃ adāsi.**and the Sangha gave him the trial period.*";
P_HTM[3039]="*So ciṇṇamānatto abbhānāraho antarā ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajji sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ appaṭicchannaṃ.**When he had completed the trial period, while deserving rehabilitation, he committed one unconcealed offense of intentional emission of semen.*";
P_HTM[3040]="*So saṅghaṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya mūlāyapaṭikassanaṃ yāci.**He asked the Sangha to send him back to the beginning for that offense,*";
P_HTM[3041]="*Saṅgho udāyiṃ bhikkhuṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya mūlāya paṭikassi.**which it did.*";
P_HTM[3042]="*So saṅghaṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya chārattaṃ mānattaṃ yāci.**He then asked the Sangha to give him the trial period for that offense,*";
P_HTM[3043]="*Saṅgho udāyissa bhikkhuno antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā appaṭicchannāya chārattaṃ mānattaṃ adāsi.**and the Sangha gave him the trial period.*";
P_HTM[3044]="*So ciṇṇamānatto saṅghaṃ abbhānaṃ yācati.**He’s now completed the trial period and is asking the Sangha for rehabilitation.*";
P_HTM[3045]="*Yadi saṅghassa pattakallaṃ, saṅgho udāyiṃ bhikkhuṃ abbheyya.**If it seems appropriate to the Sangha, the Sangha should rehabilitate him.*";
P_HTM[3046]="*Esā ñatti.**This is the motion.*";
P_HTM[3047]="*Suṇātu me, bhante, saṅgho.**‘Please, Venerables, I ask the Sangha to listen.*";
P_HTM[3048]="*Ayaṃ udāyī bhikkhu ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajji sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pañcāhappaṭicchannaṃ …pe…**The monk Udāyī had committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for five days. …*";
P_HTM[3049]="*so ciṇṇamānatto saṅghaṃ abbhānaṃ yācati.**He’s now completed the trial period and is asking the Sangha for rehabilitation.*";
P_HTM[3050]="*Saṅgho udāyiṃ bhikkhuṃ abbheti.**The Sangha rehabilitates him.*";
P_HTM[3051]="*Yassāyasmato khamati udāyissa bhikkhuno abbhānaṃ, so tuṇhassa;**Any monk who approves of rehabilitating him should remain silent.*";
P_HTM[3052]="*yassa nakkhamati, so bhāseyya.**Any monk who does not approve should speak up.*";
P_HTM[3053]="*Dutiyampi etamatthaṃ vadāmi …pe…**For the second time I speak on this matter. …*";
P_HTM[3054]="*tatiyampi etamatthaṃ vadāmi …pe….**For the third time I speak on this matter. …*";
P_HTM[3055]="*Abbhito saṅghena udāyī bhikkhu.**The Sangha has rehabilitated the monk Udāyī.*";
P_HTM[3056]="*Khamati saṅghassa, tasmā tuṇhī, evametaṃ dhārayāmī’”ti.**The Sangha approves and is therefore silent. I will remember it thus.’”*";
P_HTM[3057]="*1.13. Pakkhappaṭicchannaparivāsa**1.13 Probation for those with offenses concealed for a half-month*";
P_HTM[3058]="*Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā udāyī ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpanno hoti sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pakkhappaṭicchannaṃ.**On one occasion Venerable Udāyī had committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for a half-month.*";
P_HTM[3059]="*So bhikkhūnaṃ ārocesi—**He told the monks about this,*";
P_HTM[3060]="*“ahaṃ, āvuso, ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pakkhappaṭicchannaṃ.* **";
P_HTM[3061]="*Kathaṃ nu kho mayā paṭipajjitabban”ti?**adding, “What should I do now?”*";
P_HTM[3062]="*Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ.**They told the Buddha.*";
P_HTM[3063]="*“Tena hi, bhikkhave, saṅgho udāyissa bhikkhuno ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pakkhappaṭicchannāya pakkhaparivāsaṃ detu.**“Well then, the Sangha should give the monk Udāyī probation for a half-month for one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for a half-month.*";
P_HTM[3064]="*Evañca pana, bhikkhave, dātabbo—**And it should be given like this:*";
P_HTM[3065]="*Tena, bhikkhave, udāyinā bhikkhunā saṅghaṃ upasaṅkamitvā …pe…**The monk Udāyī should approach the Sangha, put his upper robe over one shoulder, pay respect at the feet of the senior monks, squat on his heels, raise his joined palms,*";
P_HTM[3066]="*evamassa vacanīyo—**and say:*";
P_HTM[3067]="*‘ahaṃ, bhante, ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pakkhappaṭicchannaṃ.**‘Venerables, I have committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for a half-month.*";
P_HTM[3068]="*Sohaṃ, bhante, saṅghaṃ ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pakkhappaṭicchannāya pakkhaparivāsaṃ yācāmī’ti.**I ask the Sangha for probation for a half-month for that offense.’*";
P_HTM[3069]="*Dutiyampi yācitabbo.**And he should ask a second*";
P_HTM[3070]="*Tatiyampi yācitabbo.**and a third time.*";
P_HTM[3071]="*Byattena bhikkhunā paṭibalena saṅgho ñāpetabbo—**A competent and capable monk should then inform the Sangha:*";
P_HTM[3072]="*‘Suṇātu me, bhante, saṅgho.**‘Please, Venerables, I ask the Sangha to listen.*";
P_HTM[3073]="*Ayaṃ udāyī bhikkhu ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajji sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pakkhappaṭicchannaṃ.**The monk Udāyī has committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for a half-month.*";
P_HTM[3074]="*So saṅghaṃ ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pakkhappaṭicchannāya pakkhaparivāsaṃ yācati.**He is asking the Sangha for probation for a half-month for that offense.*";
P_HTM[3075]="*Yadi saṅghassa pattakallaṃ, saṅgho udāyissa bhikkhuno ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pakkhappaṭicchannāya pakkhaparivāsaṃ dadeyya.**If it seems appropriate to the Sangha, the Sangha should give him that probation.*";
P_HTM[3076]="*Esā ñatti.**This is the motion.*";
P_HTM[3077]="*Suṇātu me, bhante, saṅgho.**Please, Venerables, I ask the Sangha to listen.*";
P_HTM[3078]="*Ayaṃ udāyī bhikkhu ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajji sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pakkhappaṭicchannaṃ.**The monk Udāyī has committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for a half-month.*";
P_HTM[3079]="*So saṅghaṃ ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pakkhappaṭicchannāya pakkhaparivāsaṃ yācati.**He is asking the Sangha for probation for a half-month for that offense.*";
P_HTM[3080]="*Saṅgho udāyissa bhikkhuno ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pakkhappaṭicchannāya pakkhaparivāsaṃ deti.**The Sangha gives him that probation.*";
P_HTM[3081]="*Yassāyasmato khamati udāyissa bhikkhuno ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pakkhappaṭicchannāya pakkhaparivāsassa dānaṃ, so tuṇhassa;**Any monk who approves of giving him that probation should remain silent.*";
