P_HTM[3180]="*Khamati saṅghassa, tasmā tuṇhī, evametaṃ dhārayāmī’”ti.**The Sangha approves and is therefore silent. I will remember it thus.’”*";
P_HTM[3181]="*1.17. Tikāpattimānatta**1.17 Trial period for the three offenses*";
P_HTM[3182]="*So parivutthaparivāso bhikkhūnaṃ ārocesi—**When he had completed the probation, he told the monks,*";
P_HTM[3183]="*“ahaṃ, āvuso, ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pakkhappaṭicchannaṃ …pe…**“I had committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for a half-month …*";
P_HTM[3184]="*sohaṃ parivutthaparivāso.**I have now completed the probation.*";
P_HTM[3185]="*Kathaṃ nu kho mayā paṭipajjitabban”ti?**What should I do now?”*";
P_HTM[3186]="*Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ.**They told the Buddha.*";
P_HTM[3187]="*“Tena hi, bhikkhave, saṅgho udāyissa bhikkhuno tissannaṃ āpattīnaṃ chārattaṃ mānattaṃ detu.**“Well then, the Sangha should give the monk Udāyī the trial period of six days for the three offenses.*";
P_HTM[3188]="*Evañca pana, bhikkhave, dātabbaṃ—**And it should be given like this:*";
P_HTM[3189]="*Tena, bhikkhave, udāyinā bhikkhunā saṅghaṃ upasaṅkamitvā …pe…**The monk Udāyī should approach the Sangha, put his upper robe over one shoulder, pay respect at the feet of the senior monks, squat on his heels, raise his joined palms,*";
P_HTM[3190]="*evamassa vacanīyo—**and say:*";
P_HTM[3191]="*‘ahaṃ, bhante, ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pakkhappaṭicchannaṃ …pe…**‘Venerables, I had committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for a half-month. …*";
P_HTM[3192]="*sohaṃ, bhante, parivutthaparivāso saṅghaṃ tissannaṃ āpattīnaṃ chārattaṃ mānattaṃ yācāmī’ti.**I have now completed that probation and I ask the Sangha for the trial period of six days for the three offenses.’*";
P_HTM[3193]="*Dutiyampi yācitabbaṃ.**And he should ask a second*";
P_HTM[3194]="*Tatiyampi yācitabbaṃ.**and a third time.*";
P_HTM[3195]="*Byattena bhikkhunā paṭibalena saṅgho ñāpetabbo—**A competent and capable monk should then inform the Sangha:*";
P_HTM[3196]="*‘Suṇātu me, bhante, saṅgho.**‘Please, Venerables, I ask the Sangha to listen.*";
P_HTM[3197]="*Ayaṃ udāyī bhikkhu ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajji sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pakkhappaṭicchannaṃ …pe…**The monk Udāyī had committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for a half-month. …*";
P_HTM[3198]="*so parivutthaparivāso saṅghaṃ tissannaṃ āpattīnaṃ chārattaṃ mānattaṃ yācati.**He’s now completed that probation and is asking the Sangha for the trial period of six days for the three offenses.*";
P_HTM[3199]="*Yadi saṅghassa pattakallaṃ, saṅgho udāyissa bhikkhuno tissannaṃ āpattīnaṃ chārattaṃ mānattaṃ dadeyya.**If it seems appropriate to the Sangha, the Sangha should give him the trial period of six days for the three offenses.*";
P_HTM[3200]="*Esā ñatti.**This is the motion.*";
P_HTM[3201]="*Suṇātu me, bhante, saṅgho.**Please, Venerables, I ask the Sangha to listen.*";
P_HTM[3202]="*Ayaṃ udāyī bhikkhu ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajji sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pakkhappaṭicchannaṃ …pe…**The monk Udāyī had committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for a half-month. …*";
P_HTM[3203]="*so parivutthaparivāso saṅghaṃ tissannaṃ āpattīnaṃ chārattaṃ mānattaṃ yācati.**He’s now completed that probation and is asking the Sangha for the trial period of six days for the three offenses.*";
P_HTM[3204]="*Saṅgho udāyissa bhikkhuno tissannaṃ āpattīnaṃ chārattaṃ mānattaṃ deti.**The Sangha gives him the trial period of six days for the three offenses.*";
P_HTM[3205]="*Yassāyasmato khamati udāyissa bhikkhuno tissannaṃ āpattīnaṃ chārattaṃ mānattassa dānaṃ, so tuṇhassa;**Any monk who approves of giving him the trial period of six days for the three offenses should remain silent.*";
P_HTM[3206]="*yassa nakkhamati, so bhāseyya.**Any monk who does not approve should speak up.*";
P_HTM[3207]="*Dutiyampi etamatthaṃ vadāmi …pe…**For the second time I speak on this matter. …*";
P_HTM[3208]="*tatiyampi etamatthaṃ vadāmi …pe….**For the third time I speak on this matter. …*";
P_HTM[3209]="*Dinnaṃ saṅghena udāyissa bhikkhuno tissannaṃ āpattīnaṃ chārattaṃ mānattaṃ.**The Sangha has given the monk Udāyī the trial period of six days for the three offenses.*";
P_HTM[3210]="*Khamati saṅghassa, tasmā tuṇhī, evametaṃ dhārayāmī’”ti.**The Sangha approves and is therefore silent. I will remember it thus.’”*";
P_HTM[3211]="*1.18. Mānattacārikamūlāyapaṭikassanādi**1.18 Sending back to the beginning of those undertaking the trial period, etc.*";
P_HTM[3212]="*So mānattaṃ caranto antarā ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajji sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pañcāhappaṭicchannaṃ.**While he was undertaking the trial period, he committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for five days.*";
P_HTM[3213]="*So bhikkhūnaṃ ārocesi—**He told the monks,*";
P_HTM[3214]="*“ahaṃ, āvuso, ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pakkhappaṭicchannaṃ …pe…**“I had committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for a half-month. …*";
P_HTM[3215]="*sohaṃ mānattaṃ caranto antarā ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pañcāhappaṭicchannaṃ.**While undertaking the trial period, I committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for five days.*";
P_HTM[3216]="*Kathaṃ nu kho mayā paṭipajjitabban”ti?**What should I do now?”*";
P_HTM[3217]="*Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ.**They told the Buddha.*";
P_HTM[3218]="*“Tena hi, bhikkhave, saṅgho udāyiṃ bhikkhuṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya mūlāya paṭikassitvā purimāya āpattiyā samodhānaparivāsaṃ datvā chārattaṃ mānattaṃ detu.**“Well then, the Sangha should send the monk Udāyī back to the beginning for one offense of intentional emission of semen—concealed for five days and committed while undertaking the trial period—and it should then give him probation for that offense simultaneous with probation for the previous offense, and it should then give him the trial period of six days.*";
P_HTM[3219]="*Evañca pana, bhikkhave, mūlāya paṭikassitabbo …pe….**And he should be sent back to the beginning like this: …*";
P_HTM[3220]="*Evañca pana, bhikkhave, purimāya āpattiyā samodhānaparivāso dātabbo …pe….**And he should be given probation simultaneous with probation for the previous offense like this: …*";
P_HTM[3221]="*Evañca pana, bhikkhave, chārattaṃ mānattaṃ dātabbaṃ …pe…**And he should be given the trial period of six days like this: …*";
P_HTM[3222]="*deti …pe….* **";
P_HTM[3223]="*Dinnaṃ saṅghena udāyissa bhikkhuno antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya chārattaṃ mānattaṃ.**The Sangha has given the monk Udāyī the trial period of six days for one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for five days and committed while undertaking the trial period.*";
P_HTM[3224]="*Khamati saṅghassa, tasmā tuṇhī, evametaṃ dhārayāmī’”ti.**The Sangha approves and is therefore silent. I will remember it thus.’”*";
P_HTM[3225]="*1.19. Abbhānārahamūlāyapaṭikassanādi**1.19 Sending back to the beginning of those deserving rehabilitation, etc.*";
P_HTM[3226]="*So ciṇṇamānatto abbhānāraho antarā ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajji sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pañcāhappaṭicchannaṃ.**When he had completed the trial period, while deserving rehabilitation, he committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for five days.*";
P_HTM[3227]="*So bhikkhūnaṃ ārocesi—**He told the monks,*";
P_HTM[3228]="*“ahaṃ, āvuso, ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pakkhappaṭicchannaṃ …pe…**“I had committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for a half-month. …*";
P_HTM[3229]="*sohaṃ ciṇṇamānatto abbhānāraho antarā ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pañcāhappaṭicchannaṃ.**When I had completed the trial period, while deserving rehabilitation, I committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for five days.*";
P_HTM[3230]="*Kathaṃ nu kho mayā paṭipajjitabban”ti?**What should I do now?”*";
P_HTM[3231]="*Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ.**They told the Buddha.*";
P_HTM[3232]="*“Tena hi, bhikkhave, saṅgho udāyiṃ bhikkhuṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya mūlāya paṭikassitvā purimāya āpattiyā samodhānaparivāsaṃ datvā chārattaṃ mānattaṃ detu.**“Well then, the Sangha should send the monk Udāyī back to the beginning for one offense of intentional emission of semen—concealed for five days and committed while deserving rehabilitation—and it should then give him probation for that offense simultaneous with probation for the previous offense, and it should then give him the trial period of six days.*";
P_HTM[3233]="*Evañca pana, bhikkhave, mūlāya paṭikassitabbo …pe….**And he should be sent back to the beginning like this: …*";
P_HTM[3234]="*Evañca pana, bhikkhave, purimāya āpattiyā samodhānaparivāso dātabbo …pe….**And he should be given probation simultaneous with probation for the previous offense like this: …*";
P_HTM[3235]="*Evañca pana, bhikkhave, chārattaṃ mānattaṃ dātabbaṃ …pe…**And he should be given the trial period of six days like this: …*";
P_HTM[3236]="*deti …pe….* **";
P_HTM[3237]="*Dinnaṃ saṅghena udāyissa bhikkhuno antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya chārattaṃ mānattaṃ.**The Sangha has given the monk Udāyī the trial period of six days for one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for five days and committed while deserving rehabilitation.*";
P_HTM[3238]="*Khamati saṅghassa, tasmā tuṇhī, evametaṃ dhārayāmī’”ti.**The Sangha approves and is therefore silent. I will remember it thus.’”*";
P_HTM[3239]="*1.20. Pakkhappaṭicchannaabbhāna**1.20 Rehabilitation of those with offenses concealed for a half-month*";
P_HTM[3240]="*So ciṇṇamānatto bhikkhūnaṃ ārocesi—**When he had completed the trial period, he told the monks,*";
P_HTM[3241]="*“ahaṃ, āvuso, ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pakkhappaṭicchannaṃ …pe…**“I had committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for a half-month. …*";
P_HTM[3242]="*sohaṃ ciṇṇamānatto.**I have now completed the trial period.*";
P_HTM[3243]="*Kathaṃ nu kho mayā paṭipajjitabban”ti?**What should I do now?”*";
P_HTM[3244]="*Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ.**They told the Buddha.*";
P_HTM[3245]="*“Tena hi, bhikkhave, saṅgho udāyiṃ bhikkhuṃ abbhetu.**“Well then, the Sangha should rehabilitate the monk Udāyī.*";
P_HTM[3246]="*Evañca pana, bhikkhave, abbhetabbo—**And it should be done like this:*";
P_HTM[3247]="*Tena, bhikkhave, udāyinā bhikkhunā saṅghaṃ upasaṅkamitvā, ekaṃsaṃ uttarāsaṅgaṃ karitvā, vuḍḍhānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ pāde vanditvā, ukkuṭikaṃ nisīditvā, añjaliṃ paggahetvā, evamassa vacanīyo—**The monk Udāyī should approach the Sangha, put his upper robe over one shoulder, pay respect at the feet of the senior monks, squat on his heels, raise his joined palms, and say:*";
P_HTM[3248]="*‘ahaṃ, bhante, ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pakkhappaṭicchannaṃ.**‘Venerables, I had committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for a half-month.*";
P_HTM[3249]="*Sohaṃ saṅghaṃ ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pakkhappaṭicchannāya pakkhaparivāsaṃ yāciṃ.**I asked the Sangha for probation for a half-month for that offense,*";
P_HTM[3250]="*Tassa me saṅgho ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pakkhappaṭicchannāya pakkhaparivāsaṃ adāsi.**and the Sangha gave me that probation.*";
P_HTM[3251]="*Sohaṃ parivasanto antarā ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pañcāhappaṭicchannaṃ.**While on probation, I committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for five days.*";
P_HTM[3252]="*Sohaṃ saṅghaṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya mūlāyapaṭikassanaṃ yāciṃ.**I asked the Sangha to send me back to the beginning for that offense,*";
P_HTM[3253]="*Taṃ maṃ saṅgho antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya mūlāya paṭikassi.**which it did.*";
P_HTM[3254]="*Sohaṃ saṅghaṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya purimāya āpattiyā samodhānaparivāsaṃ yāciṃ.**I then asked the Sangha to give me probation for that offense, simultaneous with the probation for the previous offense,*";
P_HTM[3255]="*Tassa me saṅgho antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya purimāya āpattiyā samodhānaparivāsaṃ adāsi.**and the Sangha gave me that simultaneous probation.*";
P_HTM[3256]="*Sohaṃ parivutthaparivāso mānattāraho antarā ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pañcāhappaṭicchannaṃ.**When I had completed the probation, while deserving the trial period of six days, I committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for five days.*";
P_HTM[3257]="*Sohaṃ saṅghaṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya mūlāyapaṭikassanaṃ yāciṃ.**I asked the Sangha to send me back to the beginning for that offense,*";
P_HTM[3258]="*Taṃ maṃ saṅgho antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya mūlāya paṭikassi.**which it did.*";
P_HTM[3259]="*Sohaṃ saṅghaṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya purimāya āpattiyā samodhānaparivāsaṃ yāciṃ.**I then asked the Sangha to give me probation for that offense, simultaneous with the probation for the previous offense,*";
P_HTM[3260]="*Tassa me saṅgho antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya purimāya āpattiyā samodhānaparivāsaṃ adāsi.**and the Sangha gave me that simultaneous probation.*";
P_HTM[3261]="*Sohaṃ parivutthaparivāso saṅghaṃ tissannaṃ āpattīnaṃ chārattaṃ mānattaṃ yāciṃ.**When I had completed the probation, I asked the Sangha for the trial period of six days for the three offenses,*";
P_HTM[3262]="*Tassa me saṅgho tissannaṃ āpattīnaṃ chārattaṃ mānattaṃ adāsi.**and the Sangha gave me the trial period.*";
P_HTM[3263]="*Sohaṃ mānattaṃ caranto antarā ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjiṃ sañcetanikaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ pañcāhappaṭicchannaṃ.**While undertaking the trial period, I committed one offense of intentional emission of semen, concealed for five days.*";
P_HTM[3264]="*Sohaṃ saṅghaṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya mūlāyapaṭikassanaṃ yāciṃ.**I asked the Sangha to send me back to the beginning for that offense,*";
P_HTM[3265]="*Taṃ maṃ saṅgho antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya mūlāya paṭikassi.**which it did.*";
P_HTM[3266]="*Sohaṃ saṅghaṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya purimāya āpattiyā samodhānaparivāsaṃ yāciṃ.**I then asked the Sangha to give me probation for that offense, simultaneous with the probation for the previous offense,*";
P_HTM[3267]="*Tassa me saṅgho antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya purimāya āpattiyā samodhānaparivāsaṃ adāsi.**and the Sangha gave me that simultaneous probation.*";
P_HTM[3268]="*Sohaṃ parivutthaparivāso saṅghaṃ antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya chārattaṃ mānattaṃ yāciṃ.**When I had completed the probation, I asked the Sangha for the trial period of six days for that offense,*";
P_HTM[3269]="*Tassa me saṅgho antarā ekissā āpattiyā sañcetanikāya sukkavissaṭṭhiyā pañcāhappaṭicchannāya chārattaṃ mānattaṃ adāsi.**and the Sangha gave me the trial period.*";
