P_HTM[3390]="*Suṇātu me, bhante, saṅgho.**Please, Venerables, I ask the Sangha to listen.*";
P_HTM[3391]="*Ayaṃ itthannāmo bhikkhu sambahulā saṅghādisesā āpattiyo āpajji—**The monk so-and-so has committed a number of offenses entailing suspension:*";
P_HTM[3392]="*ekā āpatti ekāhappaṭicchannā …pe…**one concealed for one day …*";
