P_HTM[4340]="*So vibbhamitvā puna upasampanno yā āpattiyo pubbe nibbematiko chādesi tā āpattiyo pacchā nibbematiko chādeti;**He then disrobes. Being re-ordained and having become sure of all the offenses, he conceals those offenses he previously was sure of,*";
