P_HTM[4449]="*Ekassa hoti ārocessāmīti, ekassa hoti na ārocessāmīti.**One thinks, “I’ll inform;” the other thinks, “I won’t inform.”*";
P_HTM[4450]="*So paṭhamampi yāmaṃ chādeti, dutiyampi yāmaṃ chādeti, tatiyampi yāmaṃ chādeti—**He then conceals it during the first part of the night, during the second part of the night, and during the third part of the night.*";
P_HTM[4451]="*uṭṭhite aruṇe channā hoti āpatti.**If he is still concealing it at dawn, he has committed an offense*";
