P_HTM[4453]="*Yathāpaṭicchanne cassa parivāsaṃ datvā ubhinnampi mānattaṃ dātabbaṃ.**He should be given probation according to the length of the concealment of that offense, and both should then be given the trial period of six days.*";
P_HTM[4454]="*Dve bhikkhū saṅghādisesaṃ āpannā honti.**Two monks have each committed an offense entailing suspension,*";
P_HTM[4455]="*Te saṅghādisese saṅghādisesadiṭṭhino honti.**and they regard it as an offense entailing suspension.*";
