P_HTM[4477]="*9. Mūlāyaavisuddhinavaka**9. The group of nine on unpurified with sending back to the beginning*";
P_HTM[4478]="*Idha pana, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sambahulā saṅghādisesā āpattiyo āpajjati parimāṇampi aparimāṇampi, ekanāmampi nānānāmampi, sabhāgampi visabhāgampi, vavatthitampi sambhinnampi.**“It may be that a monk has committed a number of offenses entailing suspension, both specified and unspecified, both of the same name and of various names, both of the same kind and of various kinds, both of the same sort and of various sorts.*";
P_HTM[4479]="*So saṅghaṃ tāsaṃ āpattīnaṃ samodhānaparivāsaṃ yācati.**He asks the Sangha for simultaneous probation for those offenses,*";
P_HTM[4480]="*Tassa saṅgho tāsaṃ āpattīnaṃ samodhānaparivāsaṃ deti.**and the Sangha gives him that probation.*";
