P_HTM[4774]="*‘ayaṃ dhammo, ayaṃ vinayo, idaṃ satthusāsanaṃ, imaṃ gaṇhāhi, imaṃ rocehī’ti.**‘This is the Teaching, this is the Monastic Law, this is the Teacher’s instruction; learn this, accept this.’*";
