P_HTM[5225]="*‘na kho ahaṃ, āvuso, dubbhāsitaṃ ajjhāpanno, pārājikaṃ ajjhāpanno’ti.**‘I haven’t committed an offense of wrong speech, but an offense entailing expulsion.’*";
