P_HTM[12269]="*thullaccayena pācittiyena pāṭidesanīyena dukkaṭena dubbhāsitena pātimokkhaṃ ṭhapeti—**for a serious offense, for an offense entailing confession, for an offense entailing acknowledgment, for an offense of wrong conduct, or for an offense of wrong speech.*";
