P_HTM[12278]="*Samūlikāya sīlavipattiyā pātimokkhaṃ ṭhapeti akatāya, samūlikāya sīlavipattiyā pātimokkhaṃ ṭhapeti katāya;**One cancels the Monastic Code, having grounds, for the failure in morality of one who hasn’t failed, for the failure in morality of one who has failed,*";
